> [@Leeable](https://github.com/Leeable) The provided payload is incorrect. The `/libpod/containers/create` endpoint doesn't support the `podman inspect` output. Furthermore, the Podman API doesn't report errors for invalid payloads (e.g., incorrect key names or unexpected values).
> 
> Barring any objections, I will close this issue.

